\[Ellipsis]}, {x, x   , x   }, {y, y   , y   }] plots several functions. \
Plot3D[{\[Ellipsis], w[f ], \[Ellipsis]}, \[Ellipsis]] plots f  with features \
defined by the symbolic wrapper w.Plot3D[\[Ellipsis], {x, y} \[Element] reg] \
