\[Ellipsis], col }, dir] draws along the straight line with a direction \
dir.LinearGradientFilling[{pos , \[Ellipsis], pos } \[Rule] {col , \
\[Ellipsis], col }, dir, padding] uses the specified padding when drawing \
beyond the boundary positions pos  and pos . \n                          1    \
