+ \[Beta]  f  + \[Ellipsis] that fits the y  for successive x values 1, 2, \
\[Ellipsis].LinearModelFit[{{x  , x  , \[Ellipsis], y }, {x  , x  , \
\[Ellipsis], y }, \[Ellipsis]}, {f , f , \[Ellipsis]}, {x , x , \[Ellipsis]}] \
constructs a linear model of the form \[Beta]  + \[Beta]  f  + \[Beta]  f  + \
\[Ellipsis] where the f  depend on the variables x . LinearModelFit[{m, v}] \
constructs a linear model from the design matrix m and response vector v.\n   \
