parameter x. {x , x , \[Ellipsis]} |->body or {x , x , \[Ellipsis]} \
\[Function] body or Function[{x , x , \[Ellipsis]}, body] is a pure function \
with a list of formal parameters. Function[params, body, attrs] is a pure \
function that is treated as having attributes attrs for purposes of \
evaluation.\n                                                                 \
