\[Ellipsis]}, {x , x , \[Ellipsis]}, dom] tests whether f (x , x , \
\[Ellipsis]), f (x , x , \[Ellipsis]), \[Ellipsis] are analytic functions for \
x , x , \[Ellipsis] \[Element] dom.FunctionAnalytic[{funs, cons}, xvars, dom] \
tests whether funs (xvars) are analytic functions for xvars in an open set \
containing the solutions of the constraints cons over the domain dom.\n       \
